<!--
Interactive Virtual Birthday Card
File: index.html

What's inside:
- Single-file static webpage (HTML + CSS + JS)
- Animated balloons, confetti, personal message for Ziad
- Clickable "Play Song" and "Blow Out Candles" interactions
- Small WebAudio melody (no external assets required)

How to use on GitHub Pages:
1. Create a new GitHub repo (e.g. `ziad-birthday-card`).
2. Add this file as `index.html` at the repo root.
3. Commit & push to main branch.
4. In repository Settings > Pages, set source to `main` branch and root folder. GitHub Pages will publish at `https://<your-username>.github.io/<repo-name>/`.

Want me to also create a README with deployment steps or a multi-file repo (separate CSS/JS)? Ask and I'll add it.
-->

